The SoC used in this device looks like a RT63363E (??) from the FCC photos, but it may instead be a RT63365E (!!).
"2011500116 Rev:1.0" is silkscreened on the board in the FCC photos. :A photo of a presumed [[TP-LINK TD-W8951ND v4]] (which is silkscreened with :"2011500107" and "Rev:1.1") is also pictured in the FCC internal photos.
